{"id": 2761, "genre": 1001, "title": "长得胖一点，你都有可能会遭遇哪些隐蔽的歧视？", "description": "即便在流行「反歧视」的如今，我们胖子们依旧生活在水深火热中。", "record_count": 2262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190128112207XKhM8b4LqHJt6lVo.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-02-01T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 327939, "content": "吃个饼\n“少吃点这个，吃这个最爱胖。”\n然后他开始吃\n\n喝点水\n“饭后别喝水，爱胖”\n然后他开始喝\n\n我问“那你怎么这么做呢”\n“因为我瘦啊”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058013}, {"id": 327172, "content": "你瘦下来可以找到一个不错的对象的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582180}, {"id": 326408, "content": "衣服不好选", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573739}, {"id": 330508, "content": "出去游泳自己看不到自己的脚…\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1599241}, {"id": 326157, "content": "再好的朋友也是没有问题和你嘻嘻哈哈实则内心完全不care你有长相这码事儿也不认为你有找对象的心和能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1574746}, {"id": 326413, "content": "你只是脸有点圆了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576010}, {"id": 326159, "content": "好白菜都被猪拱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1551435}, {"id": 326677, "content": "“你脸怎么肿了？”\n“...我只是胖了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576890}, {"id": 326166, "content": "冬天穿的多:胖子居然还怕冷！\n冬天穿的少:胖子果然不怕冷！", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541473}, {"id": 326686, "content": "买衣服时店员说没大号了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1557361}, {"id": 329768, "content": "你把肥减下来就行了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1595636}, {"id": 325933, "content": "这个只有均码诶，你ok吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568370}, {"id": 325936, "content": "别人:你就是骨架很大嘛\n我:我是肉多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522304}, {"id": 325689, "content": "“少吃点吧 就当减肥了”没人想减 我也没觉得我肥", "image": null, "praise_count": 88, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572865}, {"id": 327227, "content": "讨厌那些说着“自己的身材都控制不了，还能干什么？”的人，自以为是的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580066}, {"id": 326204, "content": "痛点啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1545539}, {"id": 325693, "content": "管理不了身材的人，还能管理什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1558143}, {"id": 326461, "content": "你坐着都长胖", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576787}, {"id": 325694, "content": "对方和你见面第一句话大约就是：哇！你好像瘦了！（对方以为这样寒暄的话 会令你开心，其实觉得在变相提醒你是个胖子）", "image": null, "praise_count": 230, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572870}, {"id": 335167, "content": "我同桌曾对我说“他喜欢你是因为你胸大，你看他这么廋，你们合适吗，你看我，比你廋从初一就有人喜欢我”我就想呵呵关你啥事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615434}, {"id": 325695, "content": "很多人觉得胖的人找不到对象，需要靠资产才有人会理睬", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572256}, {"id": 325696, "content": "没了胖就只剩下丑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698918}, {"id": 325698, "content": "被胖子喜欢的人可能也会被嘲笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 166, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570975}, {"id": 325700, "content": "衣服穿不下", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462610}, {"id": 325701, "content": "胖子饭量一定比瘦子大，然而并没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 130, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212252}, {"id": 325702, "content": "吃宵夜不带你是为你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 325703, "content": "你瘦下来肯定很好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 294, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164756}, {"id": 325704, "content": "你吃的挺多吧，你这么胖还不能吃？别装了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412144}, {"id": 325706, "content": "小尺码衣服穿不上", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216852}, {"id": 325962, "content": "胖子长得再好看，他的标签还是胖子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572204}, {"id": 325707, "content": "“薯片你吃不？”\n“谢谢啊，我不吃”\n“咋的要减肥啊？”\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572898}, {"id": 325963, "content": "每个胖子都是潜力股", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404590}, {"id": 325708, "content": "胖子没前途", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571880}, {"id": 325964, "content": "“你就会横着长，竖着怎么不长”", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573953}, {"id": 325709, "content": "我来说个相反的。胖子都是潜力股", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256841}, {"id": 325710, "content": "心水的衣服没有码", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913171}, {"id": 325711, "content": "你看你胖的，都嘬腮了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020888}, {"id": 325712, "content": "肚子真好玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020888}, {"id": 325713, "content": "不差这一顿", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020888}, {"id": 325714, "content": "是时候展示你真正的实力了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020888}, {"id": 325715, "content": "服务员:你是结巴吗？\n我:不是？\n服务员:那你要xxxxxl？", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1536315}, {"id": 325716, "content": "哪个圈子都有肥胖的人，喜欢玩游戏和喜欢看动漫的圈子里如果肥胖就会被扣帽子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026885}, {"id": 325718, "content": "每次买衣服都要跟店员说我不是个结巴\n\n我要xxxxxxx..........L号的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572928}, {"id": 325719, "content": "不吃饭说你减肥，吃一点说你这么胖还吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 124, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1526486}, {"id": 325720, "content": "买衣服的时候，店员说：“这样穿显瘦。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188634}, {"id": 328025, "content": "可能是碰到男生对自己好一点，都不敢多想，怕是自己想多了，尴尬呗。", "image": "img/option/option/201902172119191k2JhEXdycQAeBOF.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407510}, {"id": 325721, "content": "人人平等🤔🤔🤔", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1572103}, {"id": 326489, "content": "冬天还嫌冷，你长那么厚的肉是干什么的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1567315}, {"id": 325722, "content": "你穿肯定不合适", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544454}, {"id": 326750, "content": "来自男朋友无奈的眼神", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1547940}]}